data.description:
Situated in a peaceful neighborhood, this charming home offers a perfect blend of comfort, style, and convenience in the desirable Bellemeade community. From the moment you step through the front door, you'll be captivated by the warmth and character this home exudes. The living areas are designed for both functionality and style with engineered hardwood floors and ample natural light. The open floor plan seamlessly connects the living room, dining area, and kitchen, creating a perfect environment for entertaining guests or enjoying family time. The well-appointed kitchen boasts castled white cabinets, center island, granite countertops, and stainless-steel appliances. Immediately off the kitchen is a large mudroom and a separate walk-in pantry.  Also listed for rent MLS#24002148. Upstairs, the primary suite awaits with a private full bath and a large walk-in closet. Three more spacious, well-lit bedrooms with generous closets, another full bath and 2nd-floor laundry complete the upper level.
The home sits on a huge lot with an expansive new patio and lots of additional space for outdoor gatherings and pets to roam. Additional features include in-ground sprinkler system, invisible fence, Ring & Nest smart devices, and 10-year structural warranty.
Schedule a showing today to experience all this home has to offer.
